{"id":120,"ayahs":[{"number":71,"arabic":"وَحَسِبُوٓا۟ أَلَّا تَكُونَ فِتْنَةٌۭ فَعَمُوا۟ وَصَمُّوا۟ ثُمَّ تَابَ ٱللَّهُ عَلَيْهِمْ ثُمَّ عَمُوا۟ وَصَمُّوا۟ كَثِيرٌۭ مِّنْهُمْ ۚ وَٱللَّهُ بَصِيرٌۢ بِمَا يَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"thinking that no harm would befall them; and so they became blind and deaf [of heart]. Thereafter God accepted their repentance: and again many of them became blind and deaf. But God sees all that they do.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/740.mp3","surahId":5,"words":[{"id":60173,"position":1,"arabic":"وَحَسِبُوٓا۟","translation":"এবং তারা ধারণা করেছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/005_071_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60174,"position":2,"arabic":"أَلَّا","translation":"যে না","audioUrl":"wbw/005_071_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60175,"position":3,"arabic":"تَكُونَ","translation":"হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_071_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60176,"position":4,"arabic":"فِتْنَةٌۭ","translation":"কোনো শাস্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/005_071_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60177,"position":5,"arabic":"فَعَمُوا۟","translation":"ফলে তারা অন্ধ হলো","audioUrl":"wbw/005_071_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60178,"position":6,"arabic":"وَصَمُّوا۟","translation":"ও তারা বধির হলো","audioUrl":"wbw/005_071_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60179,"position":7,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/005_071_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60180,"position":8,"arabic":"تَابَ","translation":"ক্ষমা করলেন","audioUrl":"wbw/005_071_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60181,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/005_071_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60182,"position":10,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمْ","translation":"উপর তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_071_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60183,"position":11,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপরও","audioUrl":"wbw/005_071_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60184,"position":12,"arabic":"عَمُوا۟","translation":"অন্